-- seed-demo.sql
-- Demo seed data for The Maker Football Incubator.
-- Populates players, sessions, wearable data, load records, and videos
-- so all dashboard pages display realistic content without live hardware.
--
-- Run AFTER seed.sql (which inserts the academy).
-- Run via: psql <connection_string> -f seed-demo.sql
-- Or paste into the Supabase SQL editor.
--
-- For the live HR demo: call mock-hr-stream Edge Function with session s1
-- (2026-03-22 "today" session) to see the live dashboard update in real time.

