-- ===========================================================================
-- Done. Dashboard pages now have:
--   / (Dashboard)    — latest session card, 5+ injury alerts (red/amber), trend data
--   /sessions        — 6 sessions across training + match types
--   /sessions/[s2]   — full wearable data for 11 players + TRIMP scores
--   /sessions/[s3]   — match day data + Veo video link
--   /players         — 22 players across 3 age groups
--   /players/[p1]    — Ahmed Hassan profile with load history
--   /live            — invoke mock-hr-stream on s1 UUID to demo realtime HR
-- ===========================================================================
